Allu Arjun is an Indian actor who predominantly works in Telugu films. He is one of the highest paid actors in South India and is also known for his dancing abilities. Allu is a recipient of several awards, including five Filmfare Awards South and five Nandi Awards. Allu Arjun made his debut with Gangotri in 2003. Wikipedia
Born: 8 April 1982 (age 40 years), Chennai
Height: 1.79 m
Spouse: Sneha Reddy (m. 2011)
Children: Allu Arha, Allu Ayaan
Parents: Allu Aravind, Nirmala Allu
